    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is a driver-spec 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54B32 high-revving inline-six. This naturally aspirated power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system to achieve a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The longitudinal engine is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This example is mechanically robust, with a reinforced rear subframe and serviced rod bearings, addressing the primary structural concerns of the chassis. The suspension remains tight, offering the precise turn-in and communicative steering rack feedback synonymous with the M-division's peak engineering era. A well-maintained enthusiast machine with sorted vitals.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
