      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and luxury. The exterior features a deep Metallic Charcoal finish that retains a high gloss, though close inspection reveals minor, typical road peppering on the front bumper consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium leather seats show only light softening and no tears, while the wood-trim accents remain vibrant and scratch-free. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced at strict intervals, resulting in a whisper-quiet idle and a responsive, smooth-shifting transmission. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a reliable, turn-key machine ready for its next chapter.",
