      "description": "Hi there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the basics so it\u2019s ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show you around the car!",
